'''A Rahman A Jamal''' is a Professor of Paediatric and Senior Principal Research Fellow<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ukm.my/umbi/staff-department/academic/|title=UMBI Founding Director|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref> at [[UKM Medical Molecular Biology Institute (UMBI)]]. He is the founding director of UMBI.
